MSSM, unitary gauge
 Constraints 
 Name |> Expression                                                                                                      <|> Comment                      <|
pi    |4*atan(1)                                                                                                          |
CW    |sqrt(1-SW^2)                                                                                                       |cos of the Weinberg angle
S2W   |2*SW*CW                                                                                                            |
C2W   |CW^2-SW^2                                                                                                          |
MW    |MZ*CW                                                                                                              |W mass
c12   |sqrt(1-s12^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
c23   |sqrt(1-s23^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
c13   |sqrt(1-s13^2)                                                                                                      |parameter  of C-K-M matrix
