cb    |sqrt(1-sb^2)                                                                                                       |Cosine beta
t2b   |2*tb/(1-tb^2)                                                                                                      |
c2b   |cb^2-sb^2                                                                                                          |cos(2b)
s2b   |4*sb*cb/2                                                                                                          |sin(2b)
ls3   |Ml*Al/Sqrt2*EE/SW/MW/cb                                                                                            |Tau soft coupling (Rosiek notation)
