MSnm  |sqrt(c2b*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                                     |mu-sneutrino mass
MSnl  |sqrt(c2b*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml3^2)/CW                                                                                     |tau-sneutrino mass
MSeL  |sqrt(-c2b*(CW^2-SW^2)*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                        |left selectron mass
MSeR  |sqrt(-SW^2*c2b*MW^2+CW^2*Mr2^2)/CW                                                                                 |right selectron mass
MSmL  |sqrt(-c2b*(CW^2-SW^2)*MW^2/2+CW^2*Ml2^2)/CW                                                                        |left smuon mass
MSmR  |sqrt(-SW^2*c2b*MW^2+CW^2*Mr2^2)/CW                                                                                 |right smuon mass
MSlLL |Ml3^2+Ml^2-MW^2/CW^2*(1/2-SW^2)*c2b                                                                                |
